QuestData.Title: King Da'ka
QuestData.Description:
King Da'ka? More like King Dooker.
My king sent me to talk to this new king. This new king took my things and tried to take my wings.
Negotiations are ooked. Go, sticket to that angry wikket.
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: The "Big Mon" of Gorilla Gorge. Highly intelligent and dangerous.
